WEBVTT


00:01:38.879 --> 00:01:39.680
Qingqiu.

00:01:41.640 --> 00:01:42.439
Gu Zhantian!

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:43.239
Why are you here?

00:01:43.239 --> 00:01:44.280
I'm Lu Chengwen.

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:45.480
I've been face-swapped.

00:01:46.079 --> 00:01:46.879
Face-swapping?

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:49.120
Security!

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:49.879
Help me!

00:01:49.879 --> 00:01:50.079
Security!

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:51.879
Calm down.

00:01:52.079 --> 00:01:52.879
I can pro...

00:01:53.159 --> 00:01:54.239
I can prove it.

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:58.359
Security!

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:58.879
Security!

00:01:58.879 --> 00:01:59.640
Help me!

00:02:00.239 --> 00:02:01.040
Somebody!

00:02:01.879 --> 00:02:02.159
Unbelievable.

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:03.560
Playing the exact same plot twice?

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.640
Look into my eyes.

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:05.959
Qingqiu.

00:02:06.439 --> 00:02:07.879
Can you hear my inner voice?

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.159
Brother Chengwen.

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:16.719
It really is you.

00:02:16.759 --> 00:02:17.840
What is going on?

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:20.360
I'll explain it to you later.

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:21.800
Today, Gu Zhantian used my face

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:23.120
to ask Tie Tuo Wang for money.

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:24.479
Wait.

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:25.879
Didn't he just arrive?

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:26.520
Where is he?

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.960
I just sent him and that guy named Tie

00:02:27.960 --> 00:02:28.840
to the conference room.

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:29.919
Hurry and stop him.

00:02:29.919 --> 00:02:30.560
Let's go.

00:02:41.479 --> 00:02:42.680
Sign the contract,

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:43.719
and you'll be done here.

00:02:44.479 --> 00:02:45.360
Move fast.

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:46.639
I'm in a hurry.

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:47.639
Don't worry.

00:02:47.879 --> 00:02:48.960
My moves

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:50.280
have always been swift.

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:57.520
Immovable King!

00:03:06.919 --> 00:03:07.719
How dare you!

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:09.360
You dare to hit

00:03:09.360 --> 00:03:10.759
this Young Master?

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:12.840
Still dare to call yourself Young Master?

00:03:12.879 --> 00:03:14.719
The Master has already sent

00:03:14.719 --> 00:03:15.680
the Young Master's appearance to me.

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.120
You played me for a fool yesterday.

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:18.039
Now,

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:18.879
I'll let your face

00:03:18.879 --> 00:03:20.479
taste my Iron Sand Palm!

00:03:22.039 --> 00:03:23.039
It seems Tie Tuo Wang

00:03:23.039 --> 00:03:24.759
already knows he got the wrong person.

00:03:25.039 --> 00:03:25.960
Gu Zhantian

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:26.919
is really unlucky.

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.120
He's too smart for his own good.

00:03:28.719 --> 00:03:29.919
It's our turn to step in.

00:03:37.639 --> 00:03:38.479
Tie Tuo Wang.

00:03:39.439 --> 00:03:40.240
Young Master!

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.560
Smart for once.

00:03:43.520 --> 00:03:44.280
Young Master,

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:45.039
your subordinate was foolish

00:03:45.039 --> 00:03:46.080
and deceived by a thief.

00:03:46.680 --> 00:03:47.879
I hope for your forgiveness.

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:49.680
Good thing Mr. Tie hasn't signed yet.

00:03:49.879 --> 00:03:50.479
Come.

00:03:50.479 --> 00:03:51.960
This is the contract we need to sign.

00:03:52.039 --> 00:03:52.840
Okay, okay.

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:54.120
I'll sign the contract right now.

00:03:55.039 --> 00:03:55.719
Sign this one.

00:03:55.719 --> 00:03:56.520
And sign here.

00:03:56.879 --> 00:03:57.680
No!

00:03:59.759 --> 00:04:00.560
Young Master,

00:04:00.639 --> 00:04:02.039
the funds have been transferred.

00:04:02.719 --> 00:04:03.680
Does this count as

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:04.840
making up for my mistakes?

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:06.759
Idiot!

00:04:08.919 --> 00:04:10.560
Still dare to run your mouth?

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:12.919
Run your mouth!

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:14.520
Run your mouth!

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.319
I'll teach you to run your mouth!

00:04:15.639 --> 00:04:16.560
I'll teach you to run your mouth!

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:41.519
You've changed back.

00:04:42.839 --> 00:04:44.160
You still look better this way.

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:46.959
Losing five billion for nothing,

00:04:47.720 --> 00:04:49.759
and getting severely injured by his own men.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:51.879
Gu Zhantian must be furious now.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:56.079
We messed him up so badly this time,

00:04:56.319 --> 00:04:58.240
who knows what will happen next.

00:04:59.040 --> 00:04:59.839
Brother Chengwen,

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:01.680
what's so scary about Gu Zhantian?

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:02.759
Here in Haicheng,

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:04.120
we won't let him run wild.

00:05:04.279 --> 00:05:05.240
Qingqiu,

00:05:05.920 --> 00:05:07.959
you don't know how terrifying he is.

00:05:08.439 --> 00:05:09.279
Anyway,

00:05:09.279 --> 00:05:10.839
your position as CEO

00:05:10.839 --> 00:05:11.759
is safe for now.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:13.480
And I should

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:15.120
find a place to wait for death.

00:05:44.839 --> 00:05:45.639
That's right.

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:47.079
Absolutely right.

00:05:48.519 --> 00:05:49.680
This isn't a dream.

00:05:50.079 --> 00:05:52.439
It's my deepest buried memory.

00:05:52.959 --> 00:05:54.160
The exact same thing,

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:56.920
I've experienced it countless times.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.639
It's as if

00:05:59.639 --> 00:06:01.240
I'm stuck in a loop.

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:04.079
Then why,

00:06:04.079 --> 00:06:05.879
why is it different this time?

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:09.959
This is all my fault.

00:06:10.319 --> 00:06:11.959
It's my fault for not following the script,

00:06:11.959 --> 00:06:14.040
which made the plot deviate from its original track.

00:06:14.079 --> 00:06:14.879
On the contrary,

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:16.360
I even have to help Brother Zhantian

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:17.240
correct the plot,

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:18.639
to bring the storyline back

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:19.759
to its normal course.

00:06:21.879 --> 00:06:22.639
Script?

00:06:24.439 --> 00:06:25.439
Deviate from the track?

00:06:26.959 --> 00:06:27.879
Storyline?

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:32.839
Loop?

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:45.480
What?

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:48.079
Is all of this fake?

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:51.480
So everything

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:52.920
has been arranged?

00:06:54.439 --> 00:06:55.879
Then what am I?

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:02.240
Am I just a plaything to be controlled at will?

00:07:02.839 --> 00:07:03.639
Why?

00:07:04.319 --> 00:07:05.120
Why should it be this way?

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.480
Let me tell you,

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:16.079
I don't care who you are,

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.399
I will definitely

00:07:19.399 --> 00:07:20.480
dig you out!

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:31.040
Lu Chengwen,

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:36.720
I'll start with you first.

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:54.240
Why are you here?

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:55.360
Brother Chengwen,

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:57.480
I'm already homeless.

00:07:57.519 --> 00:07:59.240
If you don't take me in,

00:07:59.279 --> 00:08:00.160
then I'll have to

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.240
sleep on the streets.

00:08:03.439 --> 00:08:04.639
You have a perfectly good hotel to stay in,

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:06.079
why did you come to my place?

00:08:06.079 --> 00:08:07.160
Hurry up and leave, go on.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:07.639
Don't.

00:08:07.639 --> 00:08:08.639
I'm waiting to die here.

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:09.639
Don't come and bother me.

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:13.519
But,

00:08:13.519 --> 00:08:14.720
I'm wearing a JK uniform today.

00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:25.879
Brother Chengwen,

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:28.879
can I stay now?

00:08:30.319 --> 00:08:31.240
Aren't you

00:08:32.879 --> 00:08:34.159
tempting me to commit a crime?

00:08:34.240 --> 00:08:35.320
Aren't you afraid

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:36.200
that I might...

00:08:37.879 --> 00:08:38.679
Might what?

00:08:43.679 --> 00:08:44.639
Brother Chengwen,

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:46.519
can't you be a little bolder?

00:09:02.039 --> 00:09:03.159
So you get nervous too.

00:09:03.840 --> 00:09:05.320
Then why are you acting so tough?

00:09:06.039 --> 00:09:07.080
If you dare to bully me,

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:08.039
I'll tell your parents

00:09:08.039 --> 00:09:08.360
and have them

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:09.240
teach you a lesson.

00:09:14.159 --> 00:09:15.159
Xuejiao,

00:09:15.759 --> 00:09:17.480
why are you always clinging to me?

00:09:17.519 --> 00:09:18.600
Don't tell me it's

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:19.879
because I'm rich.

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:21.279
Head of the four major families.

00:09:21.480 --> 00:09:22.840
Once those 50 billion are invested,

00:09:22.840 --> 00:09:23.759
my family

00:09:23.759 --> 00:09:24.480
will very likely

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:25.960
no longer be one of the four major families.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.759
We might even become second or third-rate.

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:28.559
Do you know that?

00:09:28.679 --> 00:09:30.240
Then why did you still take over?

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:33.919
If I said it was for social morality,

00:09:34.519 --> 00:09:35.480
I know

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.279
you definitely wouldn't believe it.

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:37.159
I believe it.

00:09:37.879 --> 00:09:39.000
Ever since you didn't blink an eye

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.639
to destroy that batch of substandard drugs

00:09:40.639 --> 00:09:41.879
worth hundreds of millions,

00:09:41.879 --> 00:09:42.919
I gradually realized

00:09:42.919 --> 00:09:44.559
that I really misunderstood you before.

00:09:44.639 --> 00:09:45.879
You're actually a good person.

00:09:50.639 --> 00:09:51.960
Actually,

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:53.559
I'm not as good as you say.

00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:55.080
That batch of drugs

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:57.080
was also a problem I caused, wasn't it?

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:01.360
That proves

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:03.279
you're someone who dares to take responsibility.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:06.279
Do you think

00:10:06.279 --> 00:10:07.679
me investing in the South City project with you

00:10:07.679 --> 00:10:08.519
is just messing around?

00:10:08.639 --> 00:10:09.639
Aren't you?

00:10:09.919 --> 00:10:10.960
Of course not.

00:10:11.919 --> 00:10:13.440
I've studied it deeply.

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:16.120
If your ideas are realized,

00:10:16.159 --> 00:10:18.080
the economy of South City will be revitalized.

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:19.440
It's just that

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:21.879
the initial investment for this project is too huge.

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:23.840
I'm afraid before it even starts operating,

00:10:24.639 --> 00:10:25.639
your group

00:10:25.639 --> 00:10:27.879
will collapse from being unable to hold on.

00:10:28.159 --> 00:10:28.960
Xuejiao,

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:29.600
it seems

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:30.919
it seems your business acumen

00:10:30.919 --> 00:10:32.120
is also quite sharp.

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:33.519
Not any worse than Leng Qingqiu's.

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:35.440
Of course.

00:10:36.080 --> 00:10:36.879
However,

00:10:37.759 --> 00:10:39.240
I don't like doing business.

00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:42.039
Those scenes of deception for profit,

00:10:42.039 --> 00:10:43.519
I've seen too many since I was a child.

00:10:43.559 --> 00:10:45.240
But practicing medicine is different.

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:46.639
Practicing medicine can save people.

00:10:46.879 --> 00:10:49.120
Whenever I see those patients recover

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.480
and get a new lease on life,

00:10:50.879 --> 00:10:53.080
I truly feel happy for them from the bottom of my heart.

00:10:56.559 --> 00:10:57.720
But you showed me

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:59.559
what a real businessman is,

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:01.080
a real entrepreneur.

00:11:02.159 --> 00:11:02.960
Xuejiao,

00:11:03.360 --> 00:11:04.879
actually,

00:11:05.879 --> 00:11:07.840
I'm not as good as you say either.

00:11:09.759 --> 00:11:10.639
Of course you are.

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:14.240
Brother Chengwen,

00:11:16.679 --> 00:11:18.840
I really like the way you are now.

00:11:44.440 --> 00:11:45.279
Young Master,

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:48.240
President Leng and Miss Mengyun are here.